DTEND;TZID=Asia/Kolkata:20260618T210000
SUMMARY:LinkedIn — Day 30 Review Checkpoint
DESCRIPTION:Three questions only:\n1. Did any senior engineer from the 8-account list comment/react?\n2. Any DMs from technical founders\, PMs\, hiring managers referencing a specific post?\n3. Did profile views from director-level+ titles measurably increase?\n\n2+ yes → continue. 0-1 yes → adjust hooks only\, do not redo strategy.
